data.description: GREAT NEW PRICE & NEW CARPET!  Only 30+ homes in this private, gated community where this stunning home is located just minutes from Deems Recreation Center/Park, GCC, freeway access, shopping and more! Enter through your beautifully paved, private courtyard. At the front door you will discover the Casita with a separate entrance for your guests. Upon entering the main home, the very spacious formal living area and formal dining room greet you.  Venture further into the well-appointed kitchen with gorgeous granite countertops, a gas range and double ovens sure to make the chef in your family smile. Good-sized bedrooms have new carpet and en suite bathrooms. Don't worry that winter is coming - your private swimming pool is heated and ready for all to enjoy in your low maintenance rear yard The oversized garage includes a storage room which is perfect for a mancave/she shed or craft room.
